79
00:07:40,960 --> 00:07:41,980
I'm very busy.

80
00:07:43,180 --> 00:07:44,100
Good night.

81
00:07:48,990 --> 00:07:50,920
We could talk about Yang Youmo too.

82
00:08:01,360 --> 00:08:02,630
Don't let him follow me.

83
00:08:02,630 --> 00:08:04,070
Why hasn't the car arrived yet?

84
00:08:04,070 --> 00:08:04,930
It's on the way.

85
00:08:41,870 --> 00:08:43,270
Ms. Zhao, you're hurt.

86
