87
00:08:49,970 --> 00:08:52,400
[Angsana Lobby
Parking Lot
Beach]

88
00:09:06,390 --> 00:09:07,340
What are you doing?

89
00:09:07,340 --> 00:09:08,200
Go away.

90
00:09:08,970 --> 00:09:10,000
Hurry up and go!

91
00:09:11,000 --> 00:09:12,200
What's your problem?

92
00:09:20,390 --> 00:09:21,360
Dr. Liao?

93
00:09:21,830 --> 00:09:23,400
Come on, come here.

94
00:09:23,830 --> 00:09:25,030
If you're sick, go to the hospital.

95
00:09:25,030 --> 00:09:26,020
Psycho.

96
00:09:35,840 --> 00:09:37,170
What are you doing here?

97
00:09:43,420 --> 00:09:43,990
Well...

98
00:10:27,480 --> 00:10:28,320
Dr. Liao.

99
00:10:30,270 --> 00:10:31,870
Let's cut to the chase.

100
00:10:32,150 --> 00:10:33,480
Why were you

101
00:10:33,670 --> 00:10:35,550
near the spa last night?

102
00:10:38,790 --> 00:10:40,150
I don't remember.

103
00:10:43,480 --> 00:10:45,550
I just went for a walk

104
00:10:45,880 --> 00:10:48,670
and ended up there.

105
00:10:51,000 --> 00:10:53,910
You just happened to be there?

106
00:10:56,030 --> 00:10:57,160
What a coincidence.

107
00:10:58,480 --> 00:10:59,940
Is Officer Zhong alright?

108
00:11:00,440 --> 00:11:02,750
I remember he got hurt.

109
00:11:03,120 --> 00:11:03,720
He's fine.

110
00:11:03,720 --> 00:11:04,580
Just a scratch.

111
00:11:05,360 --> 00:11:08,440
When that car drove past you,

112
00:11:08,440 --> 00:11:10,640
did you see what the driver looked like?

113
00:11:23,170 --> 00:11:25,470
[November 30, 2017]

114
00:11:25,790 --> 00:11:27,720
We haven't found the car yet.

115
00:11:27,790 --> 00:11:29,320
The license plate was fake.

116
00:11:29,510 --> 00:11:31,600
And the spa's security footage

117
00:11:31,600 --> 00:11:33,670
didn't clearly show the driver.

118
00:11:35,150 --> 00:11:37,750
What did Zhao Qian
say about the crash again?

119
00:11:37,790 --> 00:11:40,440
She believes the driver was targeting her.

120
00:11:40,750 --> 00:11:42,550
But she's not sure

121
00:11:43,000 --> 00:11:44,240
if it's the same person

122
00:11:44,240 --> 00:11:45,870
who kidnapped her before.

123
00:11:48,750 --> 00:11:49,960
Has Liao Boyan left?

124
00:11:57,150 --> 00:11:59,550
Liao Boyan suddenly appeared at the scene,

125
00:12:01,120 --> 00:12:03,840
and this isn't the first time.

126
00:12:04,720 --> 00:12:07,320
Wherever there's adrenaline involved,

127
00:12:08,360 --> 00:12:09,390
he shows up.

128
00:12:11,310 --> 00:12:12,510
Captain Zheng, Mr. Zhong,

129
00:12:12,510 --> 00:12:14,310
Director Zhang wants to see you.

130
00:12:16,630 --> 00:12:17,550
A young girl's

131
00:12:18,240 --> 00:12:19,600
been reported missing.

132
00:12:21,080 --> 00:12:21,960
Young girl?

133
00:12:22,550 --> 00:12:23,360
Liu Zixuan?

134
00:12:25,550 --> 00:12:26,950
Why do you think it's her?

135
00:12:28,360 --> 00:12:29,620
Master called us here.

136
00:12:29,750 --> 00:12:31,390
It must be because this girl's

137
00:12:31,390 --> 00:12:33,850
connected to someone we're investigating.

138
00:12:34,080 --> 00:12:34,790
My first thought

139
00:12:34,790 --> 00:12:36,600
was Liu Renkai's daughter.

140
00:12:37,000 --> 00:12:37,800
That's right.

141
00:12:38,720 --> 00:12:39,720
It's Liu Zixuan.

142
00:12:42,670 --> 00:12:44,240
Some cyclists in the suburbs

143
00:12:44,240 --> 00:12:46,700
found Liu Zixuan's backpack and belongings

144
00:12:47,440 --> 00:12:47,660
and handed them over to the police station.

145
00:12:47,660 --> 00:12:48,720
[Rainbow of the Little Princess]

146
00:12:49,600 --> 00:12:52,000
The officer there contacted Sun Ting,

147
00:12:52,550 --> 00:12:54,030
but she said

148
00:12:54,390 --> 00:12:57,420
Liu Zixuan had told her earlier
about going out to play.

149
00:12:57,420 --> 00:13:00,360
She might have just
accidentally dropped her things.

150
00:13:00,360 --> 00:13:01,080
Sun Ting didn't report it

151
00:13:01,080 --> 00:13:02,200
until the next day,

152
00:13:02,240 --> 00:13:04,030
saying that Liu Zixuan
hadn't returned home.

153
00:13:04,030 --> 00:13:05,550
The police discovered in the archives

154
00:13:05,550 --> 00:13:08,150
that the missing girl's
father is named Liu Renkai,

155
00:13:08,150 --> 00:13:09,240
who had been investigated

156
00:13:09,240 --> 00:13:11,360
in the adrenaline murder case.

157
00:13:11,790 --> 00:13:13,390
So they passed the case to us.

158
00:13:35,730 --> 00:13:36,680
It's him.

159
00:13:38,790 --> 00:13:41,610
Ms. Zhao, I found
the man you saw that day.

160
00:13:41,730 --> 00:13:42,990
His name is Liao Boyan.

161
00:14:31,400 --> 00:14:33,630
[Medical Record of
Nanying Hospital, Xinggang City]

162
00:14:33,630 --> 00:14:34,240
Long.

163
00:14:34,410 --> 00:14:35,090
Boss.

164
00:14:38,920 --> 00:14:42,010
[Medical Record of
Nanying Hospital, Xinggang City]

165
00:14:51,640 --> 00:14:52,280
Boss.

166
00:14:53,480 --> 00:14:54,210
Look.

167
00:14:56,790 --> 00:14:58,320
Where's Xie Wuqiang's son?

168
00:14:58,480 --> 00:15:00,900
I heard he's still recovering
in the hospital after surgery.

169
00:15:00,900 --> 00:15:02,500
Why are you asking about him?

170
00:15:02,600 --> 00:15:04,670
Xie Wuqiang's son delivers all his goods.

171
00:15:04,670 --> 00:15:05,810
As long as we ask his son,

172
00:15:05,810 --> 00:15:07,670
we'll know if it's this man or not.

173
00:15:27,480 --> 00:15:29,790
Xie Xiaohua... seems to be over there.

174
00:15:39,480 --> 00:15:40,270
Xie Xiaohua.

175
00:15:49,730 --> 00:15:50,530
Do you like it?

176
00:15:53,140 --> 00:15:53,910
It's for you.

177
00:15:56,510 --> 00:15:59,870
Mom says I shouldn't
take things from strangers.

178
00:16:00,470 --> 00:16:01,940
I'm not a stranger.

179
00:16:02,240 --> 00:16:03,610
You know my uncle.

180
00:16:04,720 --> 00:16:05,960
Who's your uncle?

181
00:16:11,800 --> 00:16:13,240
This is my uncle.

182
00:16:13,840 --> 00:16:15,360
He has Alzheimer's.

183
00:16:15,440 --> 00:16:18,030
My family asked me to find him.
Do you know him?

184
00:16:21,320 --> 00:16:22,420
Don't worry,

185
00:16:22,750 --> 00:16:23,870
I'm a good person.

186
00:16:24,870 --> 00:16:26,030
I really need to find him.

187
00:16:26,030 --> 00:16:27,220
Otherwise,

188
00:16:27,360 --> 00:16:28,340
he could be in danger.

189
00:16:28,340 --> 00:16:30,340
Tell me first if you know him or not.

190
00:16:35,240 --> 00:16:36,510
I don't know him.

191
00:16:38,570 --> 00:16:40,260
Kids shouldn't lie.

192
00:16:40,720 --> 00:16:42,180
I really haven't seen him.

193
00:16:43,360 --> 00:16:44,480
Who are you?

194
00:16:44,910 --> 00:16:46,480
You can't just walk in here.

195
00:16:50,030 --> 00:16:50,720
I'm sorry.

196
00:16:56,970 --> 00:16:59,600
[Lyuyun Group]

197
00:16:59,720 --> 00:17:00,870
I've checked it.

198
00:17:02,030 --> 00:17:03,890
That man shouldn't be Liao Boyan.

199
00:17:05,220 --> 00:17:06,720
How could you be sure?

200
00:17:09,400 --> 00:17:10,270
Take a look.

201
00:17:10,839 --> 00:17:12,349
[Medical Records of
Nanying Hospital, Xinggang City]

202
00:17:12,550 --> 00:17:14,030
Alzheimer's disease?

203
00:17:15,069 --> 00:17:15,720
Yes.

204
00:17:16,030 --> 00:17:18,270
You might as well just say dementia.

205
00:17:18,349 --> 00:17:19,550
That's not the point.

206
00:17:19,960 --> 00:17:21,619
The point is you're mistaken.

207
00:17:21,920 --> 00:17:23,069
I'm not.

208
00:17:23,880 --> 00:17:26,210
I recognized him instantly by his figure.

209
00:17:27,000 --> 00:17:28,510
He was there when I almost got hit

210
00:17:28,510 --> 00:17:29,770
by that car yesterday.

211
00:17:30,510 --> 00:17:33,480
I can't forget the way he looked at me.

212
00:17:35,850 --> 00:17:37,650
Then why would he come after you?

213
00:17:37,750 --> 00:17:38,750
If I knew that,

214
00:17:38,750 --> 00:17:40,550
would I need you to investigate?

215
00:17:42,750 --> 00:17:44,480
Let me show you something else.

216
00:17:52,200 --> 00:17:55,000
His daughter died
in a car accident five years ago.

217
00:17:57,160 --> 00:17:59,290
This has nothing to do with you, right?

218
00:18:02,360 --> 00:18:04,400
Do you know a little girl

219
00:18:04,880 --> 00:18:06,480
named Liao Yifan?

220
00:18:07,640 --> 00:18:08,440
Who?

221
00:18:08,830 --> 00:18:09,830
Five years ago,

222
00:18:11,140 --> 00:18:15,130
she was killed by a hit-and-run car.

223
00:18:15,690 --> 00:18:16,830
It's him.

224
00:18:17,440 --> 00:18:18,480
It must be him.

225
00:18:19,790 --> 00:18:21,790
The police have asked me about that.

226
00:18:23,550 --> 00:18:25,690
So you really killed his daughter?

227
00:18:25,830 --> 00:18:27,890
I know clearly what I did or didn't do.

228
00:18:28,530 --> 00:18:31,040
His daughter's death
has nothing to do with me.

229
00:18:31,040 --> 00:18:33,970
Even if you didn't do it,
maybe someone under you did.

230
00:18:34,920 --> 00:18:37,480
You must've crossed Liao Boyan somehow.

231
00:18:38,270 --> 00:18:39,400
Just like Fang Qinchun

232
00:18:39,400 --> 00:18:42,110
came after you because of Qian Cheng.

233
00:18:51,960 --> 00:18:54,070
I already told the police
everything yesterday.

234
00:18:54,070 --> 00:18:57,080
I didn't expect you
to show up again today.

235
00:18:57,240 --> 00:18:58,110
Have some water.

236
00:18:58,110 --> 00:18:58,990
Thank you.

237
00:19:00,110 --> 00:19:02,920
When was the last time you saw Liu Zixuan?

238
00:19:09,110 --> 00:19:11,110
I think it was the night before last.

239
00:19:11,240 --> 00:19:12,160
I came home drunk

240
00:19:12,160 --> 00:19:14,070
and saw her still in her room.

241
00:19:15,960 --> 00:19:16,750
You think?

242
00:19:20,000 --> 00:19:23,240
Well, I've been arguing
with my husband recently

243
00:19:23,240 --> 00:19:24,030
and in a bad mood.

244
00:19:24,030 --> 00:19:26,830
So I've been drinking
myself into a daze every day.

245
00:19:28,640 --> 00:19:29,770
Where's Liu Renkai?

246
00:19:30,070 --> 00:19:31,100
He's gone busy.

247
00:19:31,680 --> 00:19:32,610
Busy doing what?

248
00:19:33,070 --> 00:19:34,330
Looking for the child?

249
00:19:37,750 --> 00:19:41,080
Was there anything unusual
before Liu Zixuan disappeared?

250
00:19:43,070 --> 00:19:44,240
Nothing unusual.

251
00:19:45,480 --> 00:19:48,080
What's the matter with
Liu Zixuan's injuries?

252
00:19:50,820 --> 00:19:53,310
She's a bit naughty.

253
00:19:53,310 --> 00:19:56,440
Maybe she got bullied at school.

254
00:20:01,960 --> 00:20:03,880
Why does she keep getting hurt?

255
00:20:04,830 --> 00:20:07,920
You're quite carefree
for a mother, aren't you?

256
00:20:08,200 --> 00:20:11,480
Last time you said she fell by accident.

257
00:20:11,830 --> 00:20:14,160
This time you're saying she got bullying.

258
00:20:14,850 --> 00:20:16,690
Was she bullied at school

259
00:20:17,550 --> 00:20:19,510
or was she abused at home?

260
00:20:22,680 --> 00:20:24,280
We've checked at the school.

261
00:20:24,400 --> 00:20:26,000
No one at school bullied her.

262
00:20:26,550 --> 00:20:29,270
In fact, you've got a great rep there.

263
00:20:31,000 --> 00:20:34,310
Parent representative,
giving speeches about

264
00:20:34,590 --> 00:20:37,510
"how family shapes a child's growth."

265
00:20:41,270 --> 00:20:42,400
Let me ask you again.

266
00:20:43,240 --> 00:20:45,720
How exactly did Liu Zixuan get hurt?

267
00:21:33,380 --> 00:21:33,680
[First, I must say—this is no fairytale.
This is a true story.]

268
00:21:33,680 --> 00:21:35,480
Rainbow of the Little Princess?

269
00:21:36,000 --> 00:21:37,530
One of Yang Yan's drawings.

270
00:21:57,600 --> 00:21:59,110
Mrs... Mrs. Zhang.

271
00:21:59,820 --> 00:22:00,650
Mrs. Zhang.

272
00:22:01,720 --> 00:22:04,050
We really need to ask you about something.

273
00:22:04,480 --> 00:22:05,550
Then tell me,

274
00:22:05,830 --> 00:22:08,160
when are you going to arrest Zhao Qian?

275
00:22:10,480 --> 00:22:12,080
I don't want to see you again!

276
00:22:12,550 --> 00:22:13,350
Mrs. Zhang,

277
00:22:14,480 --> 00:22:16,080
is that Yang Yan's backpack?

278
00:22:24,200 --> 00:22:25,960
Mrs. Zhang, these are...

279
00:22:28,920 --> 00:22:31,720
Zhao Qian threw away
Tong's and Yang Yan's things.

280
00:22:32,470 --> 00:22:34,480
I picked them out of the trash.

281
00:22:35,480 --> 00:22:37,920
Why would she throw away
the kids' belongings?

282
00:22:37,920 --> 00:22:39,680
I'd like to know why too.

283
00:22:39,890 --> 00:22:41,750
Why is someone like her,
who's done so many bad things,

284
00:22:41,750 --> 00:22:43,070
still walking free?

285
00:22:47,480 --> 00:22:48,510
Can I take a look?

286
00:23:05,350 --> 00:23:06,680
Can I have the drawings?

287
00:23:06,750 --> 00:23:09,810
I'd like to take them back
for a professional analysis.

288
00:23:11,350 --> 00:23:13,240
She's already gone.

289
00:23:14,110 --> 00:23:16,370
What's the point of analyzing these now?

290
00:23:16,640 --> 00:23:17,480
It might help us

291
00:23:17,480 --> 00:23:20,010
uncover the truth
about Yang Yan's accident.

292
00:23:20,680 --> 00:23:21,480
The truth?

293
00:23:22,950 --> 00:23:24,230
What truth?

294
00:23:25,680 --> 00:23:27,240
I can't tell you right now.

295
00:23:28,000 --> 00:23:32,240
Yang Yan's disappearance
is also related to Zhao Qian?

296
00:23:33,280 --> 00:23:34,160
Mrs. Zhang,

297
00:23:35,250 --> 00:23:36,440
please trust us.

298
00:23:37,240 --> 00:23:38,750
We will find out the truth.

299
00:23:58,350 --> 00:24:01,010
Kai, it's a new anti-theft lock.
I can't open it.

300
00:24:01,240 --> 00:24:01,970
Long.

301
00:24:04,120 --> 00:24:04,750
Oh my god.

302
00:24:17,090 --> 00:24:18,700
Boss, nobody.

303
00:24:28,740 --> 00:24:36,900
[December 1, 2017]

304
00:25:22,370 --> 00:25:24,570
I didn't expect Zhao Qian and Liu Renkai

305
00:25:24,900 --> 00:25:26,650
to discover me so quickly.

306
00:25:31,570 --> 00:25:33,770
But that just means they're desperate.

307
00:25:36,070 --> 00:25:38,070
And desperation leads to mistakes.

308
00:25:40,210 --> 00:25:41,930
So where are you going now?

309
00:25:44,350 --> 00:25:45,550
Where else could I go?

310
00:25:48,700 --> 00:25:50,640
I might not get another chance.

311
00:25:51,940 --> 00:25:53,300
Let me go one last time.

312
00:25:56,790 --> 00:25:57,440
Alright.

313
00:26:06,790 --> 00:26:08,400
The neighbors called the police.

314
00:26:08,400 --> 00:26:10,660
They heard someone picking the lock here.

315
00:26:10,660 --> 00:26:11,630
Watch it—

316
00:26:12,720 --> 00:26:13,750
there's blood on the door.

317
00:26:13,750 --> 00:26:14,580
Ma.

318
00:26:15,200 --> 00:26:16,640
When will the technical team arrive?

319
00:26:16,640 --> 00:26:17,840
They're on their way.

320
00:26:20,960 --> 00:26:22,960
Is the person looking for Liao Boyan

321
00:26:23,070 --> 00:26:25,130
related to Zhao Qian's car accident?

322
00:26:25,640 --> 00:26:27,790
Master, this surveillance
camera is a bit strange.

323
00:26:27,790 --> 00:26:29,350
It has infrared sensors—

324
00:26:29,350 --> 00:26:31,960
usually used for security
by elderly people living alone.

325
00:26:31,960 --> 00:26:34,140
Liao Boyan has Alzheimer's disease.

326
00:26:34,240 --> 00:26:37,240
Isn't he essentially
an elderly person living alone?

327
00:26:37,680 --> 00:26:38,270
Dajun,

328
00:26:39,070 --> 00:26:40,680
was that camera there

329
00:26:41,030 --> 00:26:43,030
when we first came here?

330
00:26:44,200 --> 00:26:45,400
Definitely not.

331
00:26:46,110 --> 00:26:47,200
Then I'll copy the surveillance footage

332
00:26:47,200 --> 00:26:48,730
and take it back to the team.

333
00:26:58,560 --> 00:27:04,360
[Criminal Investigation Division,
Nanying District Sub-Bureau, Xinggang City]

334
00:27:20,030 --> 00:27:21,590
The technical department
has compared them.

335
00:27:21,590 --> 00:27:23,650
These drawings were done by Yang Yan.

336
00:27:24,210 --> 00:27:25,880
Why would Liu Zixuan's home

337
00:27:25,880 --> 00:27:27,590
have Yang Yan's drawings?

338
00:27:28,270 --> 00:27:31,800
What could be the relationship
between Liu Zixuan and Yang Yan?

339
00:27:31,850 --> 00:27:33,590
[Criminal Investigation Division,
Nanying District Sub-Bureau, Xinggang City]

340
00:27:33,590 --> 00:27:34,880
Don't these drawings

341
00:27:36,210 --> 00:27:38,150
look like a map to you?

342
00:27:44,720 --> 00:27:46,480
If it is a map,

343
00:27:48,030 --> 00:27:50,030
there must be a destination, right?

344
00:27:53,160 --> 00:27:54,270
You mean...

345
00:27:59,860 --> 00:28:00,590
Well...

346
00:28:01,040 --> 00:28:02,170
What does this mean?

347
00:28:02,790 --> 00:28:04,310
Didn't Captain Zheng say

348
00:28:05,200 --> 00:28:07,350
the truth is found by walking it out?

349
00:28:08,270 --> 00:28:10,400
Then let's go find that destination.

350
00:28:10,420 --> 00:28:11,270
Let's go. Walk it out.

351
00:28:11,270 --> 00:28:14,200
[Criminal Investigation Division,
Nanying District Sub-Bureau, Xinggang City]

352
00:28:14,200 --> 00:28:16,660
Let's head to where
Liu Zixuan went missing.

353
00:28:27,200 --> 00:28:27,900
Ma.

354
00:28:28,160 --> 00:28:29,720
Launch the drone to take a look

355
00:28:29,720 --> 00:28:31,580
at the surrounding environment.

356
00:29:10,280 --> 00:29:11,480
Liu Zixuan's backpack

357
00:29:11,480 --> 00:29:12,940
was found around here.

358
00:29:13,000 --> 00:29:15,060
This is the big tree from the drawing.

359
00:29:33,360 --> 00:29:34,060
Here.

360
00:29:42,210 --> 00:29:45,160
Liu Zixuan must have entered from here.

361
00:31:51,590 --> 00:31:52,590
The water's warm.

362
00:31:53,090 --> 00:31:54,260
We're one step late.

363
00:32:02,480 --> 00:32:04,480
Mr. Zhong, I found a pill bottle.

364
00:32:05,270 --> 00:32:05,340
Liao Boyan's meds.

365
00:32:05,340 --> 00:32:06,640
[Azathioprine Tablets]

366
00:32:06,640 --> 00:32:08,770
This isn't for treating Alzheimer's.

367
00:32:17,270 --> 00:32:18,070
It's my fault.

368
00:32:18,790 --> 00:32:19,720
I got careless.

369
00:32:22,340 --> 00:32:23,470
It's not your fault.

370
00:32:24,340 --> 00:32:26,110
Given Zhong Ning's abilities,

371
00:32:26,460 --> 00:32:28,990
he would've found
this place sooner or later.

372
00:32:36,750 --> 00:32:38,310
Liu Zixuan knows Yang Yan?

373
00:32:38,790 --> 00:32:39,480
Possibly.

374
00:32:40,310 --> 00:32:41,630
But this possibility

375
00:32:42,200 --> 00:32:43,750
is enough to link her disappearance

376
00:32:43,750 --> 00:32:45,310
with the adrenaline

377
00:32:45,310 --> 00:32:46,720
murder case.

378
00:32:47,200 --> 00:32:49,270
Everything was premeditated.

379
00:32:49,550 --> 00:32:51,480
Everything has a cause and effect.

380
00:32:52,160 --> 00:32:52,790
Good.

381
00:32:53,000 --> 00:32:54,930
The investigation wasn't in vain.

382
00:32:55,200 --> 00:32:56,350
What did I tell you?

383
00:32:56,830 --> 00:32:58,750
Different paths
lead to the same destination.

384
00:32:58,750 --> 00:33:00,080
We've found something.

385
00:33:01,720 --> 00:33:03,550
The blood stains found
at Liao Boyan's house

386
00:33:03,550 --> 00:33:05,510
and the suspect's DNA extracted

387
00:33:05,510 --> 00:33:06,830
from Xiao Dade's mouth

388
00:33:06,830 --> 00:33:07,830
match perfectly.

389
00:33:07,920 --> 00:33:09,310
The killer is Liu Renkai's henchman,

390
00:33:09,310 --> 00:33:11,240
named Chang Long, nicknamed Long.

391
00:33:12,400 --> 00:33:15,200
Also, the surveillance footage
at Liao Boyan's place

392
00:33:15,200 --> 00:33:17,030
caught someone else we know well.

393
00:33:17,030 --> 00:33:17,590
Who?

394
00:33:17,830 --> 00:33:18,510
Liu Renkai.

395
00:33:25,510 --> 00:33:26,770
Attention, everyone.

396
00:33:26,830 --> 00:33:27,960
The situation is complex.

397
00:33:27,960 --> 00:33:30,160
First, ensure the safety of the public.

398
00:33:37,310 --> 00:33:38,480
[Welcome]

399
00:33:38,480 --> 00:33:39,350
Hold on.

400
00:33:43,720 --> 00:33:44,290
Here.

401
00:33:45,890 --> 00:33:46,610
Thank you.

402
00:34:38,010 --> 00:34:39,139
Are you full?

403
00:34:40,440 --> 00:34:41,440
Let's go.

404
00:34:49,320 --> 00:34:49,880
Hello?

405
00:34:50,850 --> 00:34:52,380
Don't clear this table yet.

406
00:34:52,580 --> 00:34:53,150
Okay.

407
00:35:23,280 --> 00:35:24,280
Long is gone.

408
00:35:24,320 --> 00:35:25,980
Dajun, we've lost the target.

409
00:35:26,320 --> 00:35:26,880
Oh no.

410
00:35:27,390 --> 00:35:27,990
Go.

411
00:35:29,990 --> 00:35:31,700
[Tailiyuan Building Materials & Hardware]

412
00:35:31,800 --> 00:35:33,180
[Welcome]

413
00:35:35,360 --> 00:35:37,190
Kai, the cops are after me.

414
00:35:37,190 --> 00:35:38,390
You need to leave now.

415
00:35:46,770 --> 00:35:47,400
Ms. Zhao,

416
00:35:48,280 --> 00:35:49,680
something's gone wrong.

417
00:35:49,960 --> 00:35:52,190
Haven't heard you call me that in a while.

418
00:35:52,190 --> 00:35:53,870
Seems like it's a big deal.

419
00:35:53,960 --> 00:35:55,960
Maybe they found out what we've done.

420
00:35:55,960 --> 00:35:56,960
We?

421
00:35:59,150 --> 00:36:00,000
Kai,

422
00:36:00,710 --> 00:36:04,400
involving me doesn't always benefit you.

423
00:36:04,850 --> 00:36:06,580
As long as Lyuyun Group stands,

424
00:36:06,920 --> 00:36:08,520
you have a chance to survive.

425
00:36:09,030 --> 00:36:10,280
As long as I'm here,

426
00:36:10,800 --> 00:36:12,960
your wife and son will be taken care of.

427
00:36:13,700 --> 00:36:15,170
Why bring up my son again?

428
00:36:16,280 --> 00:36:17,440
What do you mean?

429
00:36:19,150 --> 00:36:21,710
You're asking me for money to run away?

430
00:36:23,190 --> 00:36:24,000
What?

431
00:36:24,020 --> 00:36:25,320
One million?

432
00:36:26,400 --> 00:36:28,110
I can't help you with that.

433
00:37:22,320 --> 00:37:22,960
Honey.

434
00:37:24,760 --> 00:37:26,220
Do we have any cash at home?

435
00:37:26,880 --> 00:37:27,950
We still have some.

436
00:37:29,480 --> 00:37:31,010
I'll go back to get it later.

437
00:37:32,320 --> 00:37:33,070
Wait for me.

438
00:37:33,440 --> 00:37:34,970
I'll be home in half an hour.

439
00:37:46,670 --> 00:37:49,190
He said he'll be home in half an hour.

440
00:38:12,150 --> 00:38:14,170
Call Ma now.

441
00:38:14,740 --> 00:38:15,500
Ma.

442
00:38:16,190 --> 00:38:18,030
Isn't your car behind me?

443
00:38:19,230 --> 00:38:19,890
Master,

444
00:38:19,910 --> 00:38:23,040
Mr. Zhong said something's off
with Liu Renkai's phone.

445
00:38:23,670 --> 00:38:24,360
Go on.

446
00:38:24,360 --> 00:38:27,620
Do you really think Liu Renkai's
going home to see Sun Ting?

447
00:38:28,500 --> 00:38:29,320
Then what?

448
00:38:29,320 --> 00:38:31,550
I think there's a more suspicious place.

449
00:38:31,550 --> 00:38:33,150
Liu Renkai has another home.

450
00:38:36,900 --> 00:38:38,150
Pull over.

451
00:38:38,150 --> 00:38:40,010
I'll come and join you right away.

452
00:38:49,220 --> 00:38:50,700
[Haojia Decor Gallery
Framing]

453
00:38:56,550 --> 00:38:57,150
Ning,

454
00:38:57,150 --> 00:38:58,880
maybe we should pull over

455
00:38:58,880 --> 00:39:00,030
and wait for him.

456
00:39:00,360 --> 00:39:04,160
That's the neighborhood where
Liu Renkai's mistress lives, right?

457
00:39:05,550 --> 00:39:06,150
Yes.

458
00:39:17,010 --> 00:39:17,570
Ning,

459
00:39:18,150 --> 00:39:21,350
Master meant for you to pull over,

460
00:39:21,440 --> 00:39:23,300
not stop in the middle of the road.

461
00:39:26,730 --> 00:39:28,180
Call Liu Renkai.

462
00:40:03,980 --> 00:40:07,940
[Unknown Caller]

463
00:40:08,840 --> 00:40:09,500
Liu Renkai.

464
00:40:34,080 --> 00:40:35,400
Update Captain Zheng with our location,

465
00:40:35,400 --> 00:40:36,840
and ask him to call for backup.

466
00:40:36,840 --> 00:40:38,960
Suspect Liu Renkai is
resisting arrest and fleeing.

467
00:40:38,960 --> 00:40:42,760
Requesting backup on the section
from Gangbei Road to Xingnan Road.

468
00:40:42,840 --> 00:40:43,230
[Police]

469
00:40:43,230 --> 00:40:43,940
Nearby units are en route.

470
00:40:43,940 --> 00:40:46,600
[Police]

471
00:40:48,260 --> 00:40:49,970
Liu Renkai's heading
toward Lulin Mountain.

472
00:40:49,970 --> 00:40:51,630
He's trying to leave the city.

473
00:40:52,420 --> 00:40:55,030
Highways are locked down.
He can't get out.

474
00:42:09,000 --> 00:42:10,660
Liu Renkai, get out of the car!

475
00:43:37,070 --> 00:43:38,000
Zheng Gang!

476
00:43:38,000 --> 00:43:38,760
Master!

477
00:43:39,400 --> 00:43:40,180
Master!

478
00:43:47,510 --> 00:43:53,580
[The Perfect Suspect]
